---

<Layout title="Abhyan Portfolio">
  <main>
    <Nav />
    <section class="main-content">
      <section class="hero-section">
        <div class="heading">Abhyan Morkal</div>
        <div class="image-section">
          <img src="/hero.png" alt="profile img " width="150px" />
          <div class="sub-heading">
            <div class="sub">
              <p>Building the web, one pixel at a time.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="button">
              <Button title="useHey ðŸ—¿" />
              <a href="/resume.pdf" style="color:grey">resume</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </section>
    <section class="about-me">
      <div class="about-heading">
        <p class="about-content">
          <span>&lt;</span> About <span
            ><img src="/about-me.png" alt="aboutme-image" width="60px" />
          </span> Me <span> /&gt; </span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-para">
        <p class="about-dis">
          Hi, I'm Abhyan, also known as mr.morkal. As a Frontend engineer, I am
          passionate about creating user-friendly web applications using
          JavaScript. I currently work at Admission Anytime ptv Ltd, where I'm
          constantly learning and implementing new ideas to improve user
          experiences.
        </p>
        <p class="about-dis">
          So, if you need a web wizard who can turn your digital dreams into
          reality, I'm your guy! And hey, who knew coding could be this much
          fun?"
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="skill">
      <div class="skill-heading">
        <span>&lt;</span> Skill <span> </span> Me <span> /&gt; </span>
      </div>
      <div class="circle-path">
        <Circle />
